  CGAL::Random_points_on_sphere_3&lt;Point_3, Creator&gt;  
 

  Definition 
 

The class   Random_points_on_sphere_3 &lt; Point_3 , Creator&gt;  is an input iterator creating points uniformly
distributed on a sphere. The default  Creator  is
  Creator_uniform_3 &lt; Kernel_traits &lt;P&gt;:: Kernel ::RT,P&gt; .
  

  Is Model for the Concept InputIterator   PointGenerator  
 

 #include &lt; CGAL/point_generators_3.h &gt; 
  

