  Operations 
 

    
             
     Random_points_on_sphere_3 &lt; Point_3 , Creator&gt; g (     
    double r, 

Random&amp; rnd = default_random);     
              
     g  is an input iterator creating points of type   Point_3   uniformly
  distributed on the boundary of a sphere with radius  r ,
  i.e.  | *g | == r  . Two random numbers are needed from
   rnd  for each point.
 

     

